<div class="trialpartWrapper" style="text-align: left;">
	<p><b>Practice</b></p>
	<p>During the experiment, you will be asked to listen to English sentences. Let's practice first here.</p>

	<p>Click "Play" to listen to a sample sentence.</p>

	<%= makeSoundButton("sample.mp3") %>
</div>

<div class="trialpartWrapper" style="text-align: left;">
	<p>After each sentence you listen to, you will be asked a question about how the sentence sounds to you. Click on the numbered scale to provide your answer.</p>

	<div style="border:dashed 1px #CCC; padding:25px; height:100px; margin-top:15px;">
			<center>How negative or how positive do you think the sentence sounded?</center><br />

			<%= makeScale({buttons: ["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"], edgelabels: ["Very Negative", "Very Positive"]}) %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="trialpartWrapper" style="text-align: left;">
	<p>Good! In the experiment, clicking on the scale will automatically take you to the next question. Please hit the "Continue" button below to continue to the next section of the instructions.</p>

	<%= continueButton("Continue") %>
</div>
